u language|Telugu]]|| [[Suresh Krissna]] ||\n|-\n|| 1998 || ''[[Mangalyam Tantunanena]]'' ||[[Kannada language|Kannada]]|| V. S Reddy ||\n|-\n|| 2000 || ''[[Kunwara]]'' ||[[Hindi language|Hindi]]|| [[David Dhawan]] ||\n|-\n|| 2001 || ''[[Daddy (2001 film)|Daddy]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]] || [[Suresh Krissna]] ||\n|-\n|| 2002 || ''[[Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai]]'' ||[[Hindi language|Hindi]]|| K. Muralimohana Rao ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\"| 2003 || ''[[Johnny (2003 film)|Johnny]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Pawan Kalyan]] ||\n|-\n|| 2005 || ''[[Andarivaadu]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Srinu Vaitla]] ||\n|-\n|| 2006 || ''[[Happy (2006 film)|Happy]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[A. Karunakaran]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2008 || ''[[Jalsa]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Trivikram Srinivas]] || [[Santosham Best Film Award]]\n|-\n| ''[[Ghajini (2008 film)|Ghajini]]'' ||[[Hindi language|Hindi]] || [[AR Murugadoss]] ||\n|-\n|| 2009 || ''[[Magadheera]]'' || [[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[S.S. Rajamouli]] || [[National Film Award for Best Special Effects]]<br />[[Nandi Award for Best Popular Feature Film]]<br />[[Filmfare Award for Best Film \u2013 Telugu]]<br />[[CineMAA Awards#Best Film|CineMAA Award for Best Film]]<br />Santosham Best Film Award\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2011 || ''[[100% Love (2011 film)|100% Love]]'' || [[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Sukumar (director)|Sukumar]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Badrinath (film)|Badrinaath]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]] || [[V. V. Vinayak]] ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2014 || ''[[Kotha Janta]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Maruthi Dasari]] ||\n|-\n|''[[Pilla Nuvvu Leni Jeevitham]]''\n|[[Telugu language|Telugu]]\n|A.S. Ravi Kumar Chowdary\n|co-produced with [[Sri Venkateswara Creations]]\n|-\n|| 2015 || ''[[Darling (2015 Tamil film)|Darling]]''\n|[[Tamil language|Tamil]]\n|[[Sam Anton]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2016 || ''[[Sarrainodu]]'' ||[[Telugu language|Telugu]]|| [[Boyapati Srinu]] ||\n|-\n| ''[[Srirastu Subhamastu]]''