18|newspaper=[[CGTN]]|accessdate=13 May 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513085728/https://news.cgtn.com/news/3d3d514d7949544f30457a6333566d54/index.html|archive-date=13 May 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Notes ==\n{{NoteFoot}}\n{{notelist}}\n\n== References ==\n=== Citations ===\n{{Reflist}}\n\n=== Works cited ===\n{{refbegin|40em}}\n* {{Cite book|title=China's Management Revolution: Spirit, Land, Energy|last=Bou\u00e9e|first=Charles-Edouard|publisher=[[Palgrave Macmillan]]|year=2010|isbn=978-0-230-28545-3|location=|pages=|ref=CITEREFBou\u00e9e2010|author-link=Charles-\u00c9douard Bou\u00e9e}}\n* {{cite book|title=China's Emerging Technological Edge: Assessing the Role of High-End Talent|last=Simon|first=Denis Fred|last2=Cong|first2=Cao|year=2009|publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]]|isbn=978-0-521-88513-3|ref=CITEREFSimonCong2009}}\n* {{cite book|title=Chinese Politics in the Era of Xi Jinping: Renaissance, Reform, or Retrogression?|last=Lam|first=Willy|year=2015|publisher=[[Routledge]]|isbn=978-0765642097|location=|pages=|ref=CITEREFLam2015|author-link=Willy Lam}}\n* {{Cite book|title=China's Political System|last=Heilmann|first=Sebastian|publisher=[[Rowman & Littlefield]]|year=2017|isbn=978-1442277342|ref=CITEREFHeilmann2017|author-link=Sebastian Heilmann}}\n* {{Cite book|title=Inside the Mind of Xi Jinping|last=Bougon|first=Fran\u00e7ois|year=2018|publisher=[[C. Hurst & Co.]]|isbn=9781849049849|ref=CITEREFBougon2018}}\n* {{cite book|title=Handbook of the Politics of China|last=Goodman|first=David S. G.|year=2015|publisher=Edward Elga|isbn=9781782544371|ref=CITEREFGoodman2015|author-link=David S. G. Goodman}}\n* {{cite book|title=The Third Revolution: Xi Jinping and the New Chinese State|last=Economy|first=Elizabeth C.|year=2018|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]]|isbn=9780190866075|ref=CITEREFEconomy2018|author-link=Elizabeth Economy}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* Bougon,  Fran\u00e7ois. ''Inside the Mind of Xi Jinping'' (Hurs