series or TV Film]]\n| {{nom}}\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{IMDb name|1560977}}\n\n{{Cary Fukunaga}}\n{{EmmyAward DirectingDrama}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fukunaga, Cary}}\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n[[Category:American cinematographers]]\n[[Category:American film directors of Japanese descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Japanese descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Swedish descent]]\n[[Category:American male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:American television directors]]\n[[Category:American writers of Japanese descent]]\n[[Category:Film directors from California]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from the San Francisco Bay Area]]\n[[Category:Primetime Emmy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Princess Grace Awards winners]]\n[[Category:Sundance Film Festival award winners]]\n[[Category:Television producers from California]]\n[[Category:Tisch School of the Arts alumni]]\n[[Category:University of California, Santa Cruz alumni]]\n[[Category:Writers from Oakland, California]]\n[[Category:English-language film directors]]\n[[Category:Asian-American film directors]]\n[[Category:Screenwriters from California]]\n[[Category:James Bond film directors]]\n", "name_user": "Samee.321", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200ePersonal life:Deleted unnecessarily racialized detail", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cary_Joji_Fukunaga"}
{"title_page": "Michael Hess (rower)", "text_new": "{{short description|American rower}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Michael Hess\n| full_name      = Michael Joseph Hess\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = American\n| sport          = [[rowing (sport)|Rowing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1955|5|17}}\n| birth_place    = [[Chillicothe, Ohio]], United States\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Michael Hess''' (born May 17, 1955) is an American [[rowing (sport)|rower]]. He competed in the [[Rowing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's eight|men's eight]] event at the [[1976 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/he/mike-hess-1.html |title=Michael Hess Olympic Results |accessdate=August 25, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Hess, Michael}}\n[[Category:1955 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American male rowers]]\n[[Category:Olympic rowers of the United States]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 1976 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Chillicothe, Ohio]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for the United States]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 1975 Pan American Games]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 1979 Pan American Games]]\n\n\n{{US-rowing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|American rower}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=August 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Michael Hess\n| full_name      = Michael Joseph Hess\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = American\n| sport          = [[rowing (sport)|Rowing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1955|5|17}}\n| birth_place    = [[Chillicothe, Ohio]], United States\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Michael Hess''' (born May 17, 1955) is an American [